item.title: 【Unreleased/Unofficial (lossless)】FLAC - Camille - Camille (Unreleased Prince Project)
item.description:
These tracks were sourced from Sign O' The Times (Super Deluxe Edition), The Black Album, Partyman (Video Mix) CD Single, and the original motional picture soundtrack for Bright Lights, Big City. Rebirth Of The Flesh and If I Was Your Girlfriend were edited to be more authentic to the original "Camille" versions. Some tracks are 16-bit, other tracks are 24-bit. Enjoy!

1. Rebirth of the Flesh
2. Housequake
3. Strange Relationship
4. Feel U Up
5. Shockadelica
6. Goodlove
7. If I Was Your Girlfriend
8. Rockhard In A Funky Place
